  "description": "Prototype dashboard for NR cell DU PM counters landing in the 'ves' bucket. Built against the 2026-04-19 demo-layer schema probe (NOT yet validated against real nonrtric-plt-influxlogger). See docs/schema-ground-truth-2026-04-19.md for the query contract.",
